<ul><li>The circumference&nbsp;\(=2\pi r\)<br></li><li>The frequency&nbsp;\(f=\frac{1}{T}\)&nbsp;where&nbsp;\(T\)&nbsp;is the time for one rotation.</li><li>The speed of a point&nbsp;\(=\frac{\text{circumference}}{\text{time for one rotation}}\)</li></ul><div>So</div><div>\[v=\frac{2\pi r}{T}=2\pi rf\]<br></div>